Popular Nigerian comedian Ayo Makun, known as AY took to Instagram to share a video on how he has just bought his wife Mabel Makun and himself two cars. The comedian made sure he wasn’t left out in the ‘car spree’ as he also got himself a brand new car. Read his post and watch the visual… “Thanks to @pals_auto_sales for bringing the dream to reality.. and also to @iam_emoney1 private port for the VIP shipment clearance. Over to you @midas_interiors. May the good lord bless your on HUSTLE in double portion in Jesus name.” Watch the video below: Thanks to @pals_auto_sales for bringing the dream to reality.. and also to @iam_emoney1 private port for the VIP shipment clearance. Over to you @midas_interiors. May the good lord bless your on HUSTLE in double portion in Jesus name.Amen. Song title Famous City By Prince Micah A post shared by  Ayo Makun (@aycomedian) on Jul 12, 2019 at 9:51pm PDT Source